                            <comment id="16089827" author="mbechler" created="Mon, 17 Jul 2017 13:35:26 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Actually, this is caused by upstream changes in the OSGI DS annotations&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;// Method descriptor #33 ()Ljava/lang/&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;String&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;public&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;abstract&lt;/span&gt; java.lang.&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;String&lt;/span&gt; configurationPid() &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;default&lt;/span&gt; &quot;&quot;;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;--&amp;gt; 1.3:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;// Method descriptor #42 ()[Ljava/lang/&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;String&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;public&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;abstract&lt;/span&gt; java.lang.&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;String&lt;/span&gt;[] configurationPid() &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;default&lt;/span&gt; {&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;$&quot;&lt;/span&gt;};
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;


&lt;p&gt;Attached patch should work for both (except when there actually are multiple configurationPids defined, but the other 1.3 features are not yet supported anyhow).&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16156723" author="henningtreu" created="Thu, 7 Sep 2017 09:04:02 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Is there a plan to apply this patch and release a new version of org.apache.felix.scr.ds-annotations? We now need to provide our own AnnotationProcessor to proceed with DS Annotations 1.3.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16158288" author="kkreuzer" created="Fri, 8 Sep 2017 08:18:57 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;FTR, if anybody stumbles across this and requires a fixed version: I have published a fixed binary at JCenter here: &lt;a href=&quot;https://jcenter.bintray.com/org/openhab/org.apache.felix.scr.ds-annotations/1.2.9-AG1/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://jcenter.bintray.com/org/openhab/org.apache.felix.scr.ds-annotations/1.2.9-AG1/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Looking forward to seeing an official release of it, though!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16158309" author="cziegeler" created="Fri, 8 Sep 2017 08:41:18 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=mbechler&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;mbechler&quot;&gt;mbechler&lt;/a&gt; for your patch. It&apos;s applied&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I&apos;ll start the release process&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
